OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783693094
OL,3,CPopular beach cafe devastated by fire
OL,4,Covernight
OL,6,FA popular Cornish beach cafe says it
OL,7,Fwill stay shut for the foreseeable
OL,8,Ffuture after it was devastated by fire
OL,9,Fovernight.
OL,11,FSix appliances were sent to Beach Cafe
OL,12,FPorthtowan at around 9pm on Sunday, 5
OL,13,FJuly.
OL,15,FDevon and Cornwall Police have told
OL,16,Fpeople to stay away from the area, and
OL,17,Fresidents were advised to keep their
OL,18,Fwindows and doors shut. A cordon is in
OL,19,Fplace.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
