FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783693094
OL,3,CPopular beach cafe devastated by fire
OL,4,Covernight
OL,6,FOwners of the cafe - Jonathan
OL,7,FRichardson and Suzanne Rees - say
OL,8,Feveryone is fine and safe, and have
OL,9,Fthanked the community for their
OL,10,Fsupport.
OL,12,FJemima Rowe, owner of Porthtowan Beach
OL,13,FShop, said: "The fire service were
OL,14,Fincredible. They had it all contained.
OL,15,FObviously it's (the owners) who have
OL,16,Fsuffered the most. But no one got
OL,17,Fhurt. The gas bottles were away from
OL,18,Fthe building. All the structures here
OL,19,Fare concrete, which I think saved a
OL,20,Fwhole complex.
OL,26,@wD@PpmwD@[pn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783693094
OL,3,CPopular beach cafe devastated by fire
OL,4,Covernight
OL,6,F"You could not get a worse time of
OL,7,Fyear for it to happen two weeks before
OL,8,Fthe summer holidays. I'm so sorry for
OL,9,FLaura, Ryan, Jonathan, Sue, Claire,
OL,10,Fbecause it's going to really affect
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,F"I've just been up to the flats and
OL,14,Fthere's a lot of smoke damage, but
OL,15,Fhopefully everyone will come together
OL,16,Fand, it will be sorted."
OL,18,F"We will rebuild and come back
OL,19,Fstronger"
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783693094
OL,3,CPopular beach cafe devastated by fire
OL,4,Covernight
OL,6,FIn a statement, Beach Cafe Porthtowan,
OL,7,Fsaid: "I can't begin to tell you how
OL,8,Fheartbroken we are, but thankfully and
OL,9,Fmost importantly, everyone is fine and
OL,10,Fsafe.
OL,12,F"The support shown to us this evening
OL,13,Fhas been more than touching, and we
OL,14,Freally couldn't be more thankful to
OL,15,Fthe amazing community that is
OL,16,FPorthtowan.
OL,18,F"This has affected not just us but our
OL,19,Famazing neighbours also, thankfully
OL,20,Fthe fire was contained to the cafe but
OL,21,Fit still has an impact on them.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783693094
OL,3,CPopular beach cafe devastated by fire
OL,4,Covernight
OL,6,F"We would like to say a massive thank
OL,7,Fyou to all involved tonight, some
OL,8,Famazing members of the public for
OL,9,Ftheir fast actions.
OL,11,F"To all the responding fire services
OL,12,Fand police we thank you so much for
OL,13,Feverything and for being so supportive
OL,14,Fof us you're all amazing for what you
OL,15,Fdo.
OL,17,F"We will rebuild and come back
OL,18,Fstronger, just please bare with us at
OL,19,Fthis time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
