CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1783693094
OL,3,CPopular beach cafe devastated by fire
OL,4,Covernight
OL,6,F"Again, thank you Porthtowan for being
OL,7,Fsuch an amazing community of beautiful
OL,8,Fhumans."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
